          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-1" n="1">Here Sarum lies, who was as wise</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-2" n="2">And learn'd as Tom Aquinas;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-3" n="3">Lawn Sleeves he wore, yet was no more</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-4" n="4">A Christian than Socinus.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-5" n="5">2<lb/>Oaths pro and con, he swallow'd down</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-6" n="6">Lov'd Gold, like any layman;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-7" n="7">He preach'd and pray'd, and yet betray'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-8" n="8">Gods Holy Church for Mammon.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-9" n="9">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-10" n="10">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-11" n="11">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-12" n="12">om.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-13" n="13">3.<lb/>If such a Soul to Heaven stole,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-14" n="14">And pass'd the Devils clutches</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-15" n="15">I do presume there may be room</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-700L-line-16" n="16">For Marlbro' and his Dutchess.</l>
          </lg>
